metadata.description: Custom eslint rules for Base UI.

Anchor UI is a fully customizable component library built on top of Base UI. It offers headless ('unstyled') React components and low-level hooks, giving you complete control over CSS and accessibility features. Beautiful, accessible, and production-ready.

metadata.scriptContent: pnpm build:node && pnpm build:stable && pnpm build:types && pnpm build:copy-files && pnpm build:manifest
rimraf ./export && cross-env NODE_ENV=production NODE_OPTIONS=--max_old_space_size=8192 next build
